in inner while loops we are calculating the total nbumber of swaps
each time we try to make the chars at l and r as equal 
after each iteration of the outer while loop we only require to find the min swaps in s[lt..rt] as we have made the rest as pallindrome
this is some kind of a subproblem 
here  choosing the next first occrrence on the left or the right which can make the curr 2 as equal is the greedy approach here 
