<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
In this problem we just need to think for the end positions which item will be best to swap with minimun swaps. For example, if we have string "aaccbb", we need to think that which operation will result into minimum swaps: 

1) swapping a with nearest b 
